a &amp;amp; b \\ 
c &amp;amp; d
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix} 
0 \\ 
1
\end{bmatrix}
=
\begin{bmatrix} 
- \sin \theta \\
\cos \theta
\end{bmatrix}
\quad \to \quad
b = - \sin \theta
\quad, 
d = \cos \theta
