\begin{pmatrix}
x_a \\
y_a \\
z_a 
\end{pmatrix}
\cdot
\begin{pmatrix}
x_b \\
y_b \\
z_b 
\end{pmatrix}
= x_a x_b + y_a y_b + z_a z_b
